ExecDesc.value: Oracle Database Server Workspace Manager Multiple SQL Injection

EngDesc.value: Multiple SQL injection vulnerabilities exist in Oracle Database Server product. The vulnerabilities are due to insufficient sanitization of input parameters in the Oracle Workspace Manager component. A remote attacker with valid user credentials may leverage these vulnerabilities to inject and execute SQL code with escalated privileges of SYS or WMSYS account. Successful exploitation would result in disclosure of sensitive information, and modification or manipulation of the data in the underlying database.
